/*
    mixi2blogger
    A firefox extention to convert Mixi diary to Google Blogger's posts.
    Author :  Ats Oka (I am from Japan)
    Website : http://ats.oka.nu/  https://github.com/ats4u
    mailto : ats.creativity@gmail.com
    日本語説明あり 下部参照
*/

/* How it works */

This is a tool to convert each diary entries in a Japanese social network
service "Mixi" into Google Blogger's post entries.

/* Preconditions */

Following accounts are necessary to run mixi2blogger :

- a Mixi account
- a Google account
- at least one Blogger blog
- a Picasa Album account


/* Files */

- mixi2blogger-main.js
    Create and initialize a mixi2blogger instance.
- mixi2blogger.js
    The implementation of mixi2blogger.
- dstorage.js
    An alternative object of 'localStorage' for Firefox which stores its data
    in specific directory.
- h2z.js
    A function to convert Japanese character.
- ltype.js
    An interface based type management system.
- reprogress.js
    A utility to calculate the proper position of a progress bar.
- tloop.js
    A function which enables loops to execute asynchronously

- BUILD.sh
    A bash script to build mixi2blogger.xpi



